"On IRC, irc.libera.chat #kde or via email, kde-graphics-devel@kde.org or on "
"the web, &lt;<ulink url=\"https://apps.kde.org/spectacle\">https://apps.kde."
"org/spectacle</ulink>&gt;"
msgstr ""
"IRC पर, irc.libera.chat #kde या ईमेल के माध्यम से, kde-graphics-devel@kde.org या "
"वेब पर, &lt;<ulink url=\"https://apps.kde.org/spectacle\">https://apps.kde."
"org/spectacle</ulink>&gt;"

